# GetFit quiz — mass edit (1min.to)

The GetFit quiz is **one shared implementation** cloned to many URL paths. Do **not** edit a single path’s `index.html` for copy/logic/style changes.

## Source of truth (edit these)

- `public/shared/getfit-quiz.js` — quiz markup + behavior + `redirect_url`
- `public/shared/getfit-quiz.css` — styles

Then commit and push `main` (Cloudflare Pages auto-deploys).

## Path shells (do not hand-edit content here)

Thin identical loaders only. Listed in `scripts/getfit-paths.txt`:

`getfit`, `getstarted`, `signup`, `startnow`, `getyourplan`, `findyourfit`, `getresults`, `takethequiz`, `seeoptions`, `findout`

Each is `public/<slug>/index.html` → loads `/shared/getfit-quiz.css` + `/shared/getfit-quiz.js`.

## Add a new path

1. Append slug to `scripts/getfit-paths.txt`
2. Run `./scripts/sync-getfit-paths.sh`
3. Commit + push

